The files are "rar" files. You need a program like winrar to open them.
First you install winrar (or other) then double click the first rar-file. You should see a window where there is a file called "sub-tsm.sefi.img".
Press "extract to" and select the folder where you want the bin-file to go.
Then you can mount the image file to a virtual cd/dvd-drive like daemon tools or burn it to a disc. Remember to use "burn image to disc" function when you burn it. If you just burn the img-file to disc you won't be able to play it in your dvd-player.
